+## Stage netlist extraction
+
+`write_netlist.tcl` extracts a LEC-comparable Verilog netlist from an ORFS
+stage `.odb` (physical-only masters removed). Wire it with `orfs_run`:
+
+```starlark
+load("@bazel-orfs//:openroad.bzl", "orfs_run")
+
+orfs_run(
+    name = "gcd_floorplan_lec_v",
+    src = ":gcd_floorplan",
+    script = "@bazel-orfs-lec//:write_netlist.tcl",
+    outs = ["results/asap7/gcd/base/2_floorplan_lec.v"],
+)
+```
+
+The output is written as `<odb stem>_lec.v` in the stage's results
+directory. Hierarchical designs (`OPENROAD_HIERARCHICAL=1`) are read with
+`-hier` and produce hierarchical netlists.
+
